<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #f59e0b; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .reminder-box { background-color: #fef3c7; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; margin: 15px 0; }
    .button { background-color: #f59e0b; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üìç Location Update Reminder</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= @messenger.name %>,</p>
      
      <div class="reminder-box">
        <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Please update your current location</strong></p>
        <p>We haven't received a location update from you recently. Keeping your location updated helps us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Assign tasks more efficiently</li>
          <li>Provide accurate ETAs to customers</li>
          <li>Track deliveries in real-time</li>
          <li>Improve overall service quality</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <center>
        <a href="<%= root_url %>" class="button">Update Location Now</a>
      </center>
      
      <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
        <small>If you're experiencing technical issues, please contact support.</small>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>FastePost Delivery System</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
